org.phantomapi.clust

  • Packages that use org.phantomapi.clust 
    Package Description
    org.phantomapi
    Contains the base Phantom class which is very useful
    org.phantomapi.blockmeta
    Used for nesting data into blocks and chunks.
    org.phantomapi.chromatic
    Chomatic blocks which supply face-specific coloring and alpha layering for blending along with what color is seen from a given location
    org.phantomapi.clust
    Contains a rubust, powerful configuration and key value data storage system
    org.phantomapi.construct
    Used for constructing structured plugins
    org.phantomapi.core
    The core set of controllers phantom uses to host the framework
    org.phantomapi.game
    Full game api system
    org.phantomapi.hive  
    org.phantomapi.hud
    Create gui applications from the running jvm
    org.phantomapi.inventory
    Inventory wrappers used for the stack api along with other utils
    org.phantomapi.lang
    Many objects for holding data in faster, easier ways.
    org.phantomapi.nest
    Used for nesting data into blocks and chunks.
    org.phantomapi.ppa
    Send and receive information through servers without the need of bungeecord or online players
    org.phantomapi.stack
    Stackapi for using a force-set no cloning system for item stacks and inventories
    org.phantomapi.statistics
    Statistics and analytical object interfaces
    org.phantomapi.text
    Formatted text, Raw Text, Message builders, Tabulators and more.
    org.phantomapi.transmit
    Transmission apis for transmitting bungeecord data better
    org.phantomapi.util
    The most useful package.
    org.phantomapi.world
    World wrappers, async utilities, object representations and so much more.
